<p style="font-size:11px;color:#888;text-align:center;">HCI Construction OS &nbsp;|&nbsp; Bid Leveling Engine &nbsp;|&nbsp; ${dateStr} &nbsp;|&nbsp; DRAFT — No Awards, Budgets, or Commitments</p>
</div>`;

